                            <comment id="14333862" author="thobbs" created="Mon, 23 Feb 2015 21:47:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=Zariel&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;zariel&quot;&gt;Zariel&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since this issue appears to also affect 2.0 and 2.1, I&apos;ve attached backported versions of the patch.  I also made the following changes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fix bugs where wrapped ErrorMessages were not actually thrown&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Only catch ProtocolException instead of Throwable when looking up opcode&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add two test cases for other protocol errors&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Minor code style and license header cleanup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Would you mind reviewing the new patches?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14335025" author="zariel" created="Tue, 24 Feb 2015 15:54:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good to me, do you want me to update the patch for trunk to match your changes?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14340932" author="thobbs" created="Fri, 27 Feb 2015 22:21:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No, that&apos;s fine, it&apos;s easy to merge the 2.1 patch to trunk.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll consider that a +1, then.  Committed as 5654e736.  Thanks again!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
